===Noun===
[[Category:English nouns]]
'''arbitrage'''

#<!--DefA--> the practice of quickly buying and selling foreign currencies in different markets in order to make a profit
#<!--DefB--> the purchase of the stock of a future takeover target, with the expectation that the stock will be sold to the person executing the takeover at a higher price

